{"word":"G3366 - μηδέ - mēdé - may-deh' - Neither","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μηδέ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">mēdé</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">may-deh'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Neither</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"அல்லவா, ஆவது, ஆமல் - எதிர்மறை மாற்றான எச்சம்"},{"paragraph":"but not, and not, neither, not even"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3361 - μή - mḗ - may/3361\">G3361</a> and <a href=\"#/G1161 - δέ - dé - deh/1161\">G1161</a>; <i>but not</i>, <i>not even</i>; in a continued negation, <i>nor:</i> - neither, nor (yet), (no) not (once, so much as).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}